     C* PICKUP DATE
     C           *IN98     IFEQ *OFF
     C*
     C                     Z-ADD1         X
TCHK2C*          'PICKUP D'SCAN DAT1      X              10
TCHK2C           'PICKUP'  SCAN DAT1      X              10
